    {
      "id": "6c5a249d_1ab7b4fd",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "message": "The sdc-cs job is not running due to size limit violations:\n```\nContainer runtime did not kill the pod within specified grace period.\nSource\nkubelet compute02-daily-master-sm\nCount\n1\nSub-object\nLast seen\n2025-03-05T17:13:59+01:00\nUsage of EmptyDir volume \"onap-sdc-cs-writable-scripts\" exceeds the limit \"600Mi\".\nSource\nkubelet compute02-daily-master-sm\nCount\n1\nSub-object\nLast seen\n2025-03-05T17:13:49+01:00\n```",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2679,
        "name": "Andreas Geissler",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "andreas@geisibee.de",
        "username": "andreasgeissler"
      },
      "updated": "2025-03-05 16:16:25.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
